dcterms:description: ModelNet40 dataset includes 12311 synthetic CAD models from 40 object categories, with 9843 models for training and 2468 for testing. It is used for evaluating point-to-plane registration methods.
dcterms:title: ModelNet40

dcterms:description: ICL-NUIM dataset consists of simulated scans of indoor scenes, providing 1278 training samples and 200 evaluation samples. It is used for evaluating point-to-plane registration methods with noisy point normals.
dcterms:title: ICL-NUIM
